Thank you.

473
00:31:54,000 --> 00:31:56,000
Mal ava be, saet xweş. Tu bi xêr hatî.
 
Thank you, have a good time. You are welcome.

474
00:31:56,000 --> 00:31:59,000
Saet xweş, em bixêr hatin qanala we dikin, herin bi selamet.
 
Have a good time, we welcome your channel, go in safety.

475
00:31:59,000 --> 00:32:14,000
Spas dar im.
 
Thank you.

