to raise it... then we make it... we crush it... we put it
in our jars...

494
00:33:42,000 --> 00:33:44,000
Zeyta xwe dikin ser.
 
We pour our oil on top.

495
00:33:44,000 --> 00:33:49,000
Û amade kin mûnetê qaçkên xwe, malê xwe, zivistanê amade
kin.
 
And we prepare the provisions for our kids, our house, we
prepare them for winter.

496
00:33:49,000 --> 00:33:52,000
